Using the :ref:`Display driver API <zephyr:display_api>` with chosen
display. That is:

| :hwftlbl-scr:`LCD` : :devicetree:`chosen { zephyr,display = &lcd_panel; };`
| :hwftlbl-scr:`ST7789V` : :devicetree:`lcd_panel: &st7789v_240x240ls {};`

